00:00:19.930 --> 00:00:20.930
Mirrored Wardrobes

00:00:20.930 --> 00:00:23.040
Mirrored wardrobes are perfect for small rooms
as they give an illusion of space

00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:25.450
The mirrored section of the wardrobe helps
the light to bounce around the room

00:00:25.450 --> 00:00:27.340
Giving the appearance of it being larger than
it actually is

00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:28.540
Many mirrored wardrobes have patterns and
styles

00:00:28.540 --> 00:00:29.920
It doesn't have to be plain and monotone

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:31.810
The greatest thing about mirrored wardrobes
is the space illusion created

00:00:31.810 --> 00:00:33.530
This can be seen in any room, large or small

00:00:33.530 --> 00:00:36.110
They help to brighten up your room by mixing
natural light with the artificial light

00:00:36.110 --> 00:00:39.331
Not only do mirrored wardrobes create more
light but they also save space in a room

00:00:39.331 --> 00:00:40.840
As you will not have a need for a free standing
full length mirror

00:00:40.840 --> 00:00:41.910
Mirrored wardrobes can be seen as a blank
canvas

00:00:41.910 --> 00:00:46.350
You can make them a focal point of the room
or create your own style around them

00:00:46.350 --> 00:00:57.500
Given that the wardrobes will reflect the
decor of your room

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:17.140
you can rest assured that they will complement
your style, no matter what that may be!

